This repo is for the "Hitting the Limits" Session at Cactusforce 2026. 
You can simply copy the code in here to recreate -- but use a different Trigger Framework or else convert the Apex Handler classes to Triggers. 
Unlocked Package Information for "Hitting the Limits" Session at Cactusforce 2026.  If you use the unlocked package, it has dependency on Best Practices Toolkit Trigger Framework. 
First install trial for "Best Practices Toolkit" (v102.0.0) on AppExchange unless you want to use your own TriggerHandler framework or else copy the Apex class code into a Trigger
Package Install URL: https://login.salesforce.com/packaging/installPackage.apexp?p0=04tbV0000000UFpQAM
